OL,3,CWildfire spreads through grassland at
OL,4,CLeicestershire quarry
OL,6,FFirefighters remain on the scene
OL,7,Ffollowing a huge wildfire that broke
OL,8,Fout in Leicestershire.
OL,10,FFire crews worked through Thursday
OL,11,Fnight and into Friday morning to
OL,12,Ftackle the blaze in the grassland at
OL,13,FBardon Hill Quarry.
OL,15,FGrassland, tress and bushes were set
OL,16,Falight as the fire spread. Crews along
OL,17,Fwith six fire engines, a water
OL,18,Fcarrier, a fogging unit and a command
OL,19,Fvehicle were sent to tackle the fire.
